data.description: Step into this charming residence that boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2-car garage. The open floor plan seamlessly connects with a generously sized backyard. Conveniently located near schools, restaurants, shopping centers, and just minutes away from Horizon Boulevard, this home, making it a definite must-see. Notably, a new roof was installed in December 2023. Welcome to your new home!
